程序包 com.google.gson.internal

Do NOT use any class in this package as they are meant for internal use in Gson.

请参阅: 说明

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    ObjectConstructor<T>
    Defines a generic object construction factory.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    $Gson$Preconditions
    A simple utility class used to check method Preconditions.
    $Gson$Types
    Static methods for working with types.
    ConstructorConstructor
    Returns a function that can construct an instance of a requested type.
    Excluder
    This class selects which fields and types to omit.
    JsonReaderInternalAccess
    Internal-only APIs of JsonReader available only to other classes in Gson.
    LazilyParsedNumber
    This class holds a number value that is lazily converted to a specific number type
    LinkedHashTreeMap<K,V>
    A map of comparable keys to values.
    LinkedTreeMap<K,V>
    A map of comparable keys to values.
    Primitives
    Contains static utility methods pertaining to primitive types and their corresponding wrapper types.
    Streams
    Reads and writes GSON parse trees over streams.
    UnsafeAllocator
    Do sneaky things to allocate objects without invoking their constructors.

程序包com.google.gson.internal的说明

Do NOT use any class in this package as they are meant for internal use in Gson. These classes will very likely change incompatibly in future versions. You have been warned.
